[
  {
    "startTime": 0.16,
    "endTime": 2.08,
    "text": "there is plenty of advice for how to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.08,
    "endTime": 4.16,
    "text": "improve your sleep"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.16,
    "endTime": 7.04,
    "text": "go to bed at the same time avoid digital"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.04,
    "endTime": 7.68,
    "text": "screens"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.68,
    "endTime": 10.96,
    "text": "after dark and don't hit snooze"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.96,
    "endTime": 12.559,
    "text": "but it all comes down to the same"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.559,
    "endTime": 15.2,
    "text": "assumption that you're doing something"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.2,
    "endTime": 16.4,
    "text": "wrong"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.4,
    "endTime": 19.199,
    "text": "when in fact it may not be your fault at"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.199,
    "endTime": 21.439,
    "text": "all"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.92,
    "endTime": 26.64,
    "text": "inside practically every organism on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.64,
    "endTime": 27.199,
    "text": "earth"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.199,
    "endTime": 30.32,
    "text": "there's a clock that keeps order known"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.32,
    "endTime": 32.719,
    "text": "as the circadian rhythm"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.719,
    "endTime": 35.12,
    "text": "for humans it's located in the part of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.12,
    "endTime": 37.92,
    "text": "our brain called the hypothalamus"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.92,
    "endTime": 39.76,
    "text": "and while it's most famous for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.76,
    "endTime": 42.399,
    "text": "controlling our sleep cycles"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.399,
    "endTime": 44.559,
    "text": "it's also responsible for helping"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.559,
    "endTime": 46.8,
    "text": "primary organs like the brain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.8,
    "endTime": 49.84,
    "text": "heart and lungs work in harmony"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.84,
    "endTime": 52.399,
    "text": "but not everyone's circadian rhythm is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.399,
    "endTime": 54.239,
    "text": "the same"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.239,
    "endTime": 56.879,
    "text": "night owls for instance generally feel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.879,
    "endTime": 60.32,
    "text": "tired later than early birds"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.32,
    "endTime": 62.48,
    "text": "often because they produce high amounts"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.48,
    "endTime": 64.64,
    "text": "of the sleep hormone melatonin"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.64,
    "endTime": 67.68,
    "text": "later at night and for most of human"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.68,
    "endTime": 70.0,
    "text": "history that didn't matter"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 71.84,
    "text": "since night owls could protect their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.84,
    "endTime": 74.32,
    "text": "tribes from nocturnal predators or their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.32,
    "endTime": 77.04,
    "text": "cities from cunning conquerors"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.04,
    "endTime": 79.6,
    "text": "but society has made it a problem in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.6,
    "endTime": 81.84,
    "text": "recent decades"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.84,
    "endTime": 84.24,
    "text": "an estimated 80 percent of americans"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.24,
    "endTime": 86.64,
    "text": "follow daily schedules that fall between"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.64,
    "endTime": 90.079,
    "text": "6 a.m and 6 p.m yet"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.079,
    "endTime": 92.0,
    "text": "nearly a third of the population"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 93.2,
    "text": "considers themselves"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.2,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "night owls which means they're better"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.0,
    "endTime": 98.84,
    "text": "off with a schedule that looks more like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.84,
    "endTime": 102.88,
    "text": "this this phenomenon is called social"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.88,
    "endTime": 104.479,
    "text": "jet lag"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.479,
    "endTime": 106.399,
    "text": "it's like the jet lag you feel after a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.399,
    "endTime": 107.84,
    "text": "long plane trip"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.84,
    "endTime": 110.159,
    "text": "but worse because it doesn't disappear"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.159,
    "endTime": 112.479,
    "text": "after a few days"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.479,
    "endTime": 115.119,
    "text": "and social jet lag is taking its toll on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.119,
    "endTime": 117.2,
    "text": "the night owls of the world"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.2,
    "endTime": 119.52,
    "text": "because even if you get the recommended"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.52,
    "endTime": 120.799,
    "text": "amount of sleep"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.799,
    "endTime": 122.799,
    "text": "knocking your circadian rhythm out of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.799,
    "endTime": 125.36,
    "text": "whack has consequences"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.36,
    "endTime": 128.16,
    "text": "for example one study found that for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.16,
    "endTime": 130.399,
    "text": "every hour your circadian rhythm is out"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.399,
    "endTime": 131.2,
    "text": "of sync"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.2,
    "endTime": 135.52,
    "text": "your risk of obesity increases by 33"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.52,
    "endTime": 137.599,
    "text": "also increasing your risk of the many"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.599,
    "endTime": 139.68,
    "text": "health complications associated with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.68,
    "endTime": 140.72,
    "text": "obesity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.72,
    "endTime": 142.879,
    "text": "and the problem isn't just a physical"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.879,
    "endTime": 144.959,
    "text": "one in another study"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.959,
    "endTime": 147.28,
    "text": "people whose circadian rhythms were more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.28,
    "endTime": 148.0,
    "text": "than two"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.0,
    "endTime": 150.959,
    "text": "hours off reported notably more severe"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.959,
    "endTime": 153.04,
    "text": "symptoms of depression"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.04,
    "endTime": 155.28,
    "text": "and since your circadian rhythm tends to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.28,
    "endTime": 156.8,
    "text": "shift as you age"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.8,
    "endTime": 159.599,
    "text": "social jet lag is especially apparent in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.599,
    "endTime": 161.04,
    "text": "teens"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.04,
    "endTime": 164.239,
    "text": "in fact the cdc warns that most public"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.239,
    "endTime": 165.04,
    "text": "schools across"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.04,
    "endTime": 169.04,
    "text": "america start too early before 8 30"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.04,
    "endTime": 171.36,
    "text": "which according to the non-profit rand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.36,
    "endTime": 172.239,
    "text": "corporation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.239,
    "endTime": 174.72,
    "text": "is costing the country nine billion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.72,
    "endTime": 175.92,
    "text": "dollars a year"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.92,
    "endTime": 178.239,
    "text": "from mainly lost academic performance"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.239,
    "endTime": 180.72,
    "text": "and car crashes from tired teens behind"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.72,
    "endTime": 182.0,
    "text": "the wheel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.0,
    "endTime": 184.72,
    "text": "luckily the circadian rhythm isn't set"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.72,
    "endTime": 186.239,
    "text": "in stone"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.239,
    "endTime": 188.48,
    "text": "turns out it's largely triggered by"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.48,
    "endTime": 191.12,
    "text": "light signals that strike your eye"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.12,
    "endTime": 193.599,
    "text": "so when you first wake up get outside"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.599,
    "endTime": 195.04,
    "text": "and soak up some morning"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.04,
    "endTime": 197.84,
    "text": "sun or if that's out of the question"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.84,
    "endTime": 200.239,
    "text": "make sure your home is well lit"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.239,
    "endTime": 201.92,
    "text": "it might just brighten your morning a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.92,
    "endTime": 203.84,
    "text": "little more"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.84,
    "endTime": 205.76,
    "text": "we'd like to learn what you want to know"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.76,
    "endTime": 207.44,
    "text": "about the human body"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.44,
    "endTime": 209.36,
    "text": "tell us in the comments and thanks for"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.36,
    "endTime": 212.239,
    "text": "watching"
  }
]